usage:
    hop check [--platform <target>] [--arch <name>] [--cache-dir <dir>] [--diag-format <text|jsonl>] [--no-import] <pkgdir|srcfile>

options:
    --platform <target>   target platform
    --arch <name>         target architecture
    --cache-dir <dir>     compiler cache directory
    --diag-format <fmt>   diagnostics output format (`text` or `jsonl`)
    --no-import           typecheck one source file without package imports

<target> is one of: cli-libc (default), cli-eval, wasm-min, playbit
